It offers the home-baked element, in addition to restaurant food, where meals can be ordered and delivered to one&#x2019;s doorstep with just a search and a click. The search engine optimisation allows one to search by category for pastas, pizzas, burgers, roasted meals and more. Beverages are presented on the platform and they too come in an array of categories. In addition, the site offers products and snacks, Banting products, spices, cheese, sauces and breads. One can also order pet food, products and snacks and have all delivered at the same time. Franchise opportunities that will give entrepreneurs the prospect of owning a piece of the R3 million platform will be available. For more information, click here www.iamcooking.co.za or on Google Play.